&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://yongchen.org/posts/matlab-3d-plot/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>matlab</category><guid>http://yongchen.org/posts/matlab-3d-plot/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 May 2016 12:02:10 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Julia Notes</title><link>http://yongchen.org/posts/julia-notes/</link><dc:creator>YONG</dc:creator><description>&lt;div class="section" id="id1"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;安装&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;下载并安装64-bit Julia (command line version), 可选择自定义的安装路径.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;新建环境变量 &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;JULIA_HOME&lt;/tt&gt;, 并指向 &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;Julia&lt;/tt&gt; 的 &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;\bin&lt;/tt&gt; 目录.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在 &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;PATH&lt;/tt&gt; 环境变量下添加 &lt;tt class="docutils literal"&gt;%JULIA_HOME%&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://yongchen.org/posts/julia-notes/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (1 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>julia</category><guid>http://yongchen.org/posts/julia-notes/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 24 May 2016 04:22:41 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Angle between 2 Vectors</title><link>http://yongchen.org/posts/angle-between-2-vectors/</link><dc:creator>YONG</dc:creator><description>&lt;div class="section" id="id1"&gt;
